      "title": "Thank you Dallas beauty",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dallas Alagaperuma thanked him for recommending the name to run in the election to elect the new president.",
        "Member of Parliament Dallas Alagaperuma posted this on his official Twitter page.",
        "Meanwhile, Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has proposed the name of the Dallas beauty to contest the elections to elect the interim president.",
        "Following this, the name of Member of Parliament Dulles Alagaperuma was named by Member of Parliament G.L. It is significant that Peirce has suggested. (a)"
      ],
